        <updateDate>2024-09-23T18:27:00Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>Ensuring No Devices Bear Your Own Data Act or the END BYOD Act&nbsp;</strong></p><p>This bill prohibits Internal Revenue Service employees, contractors, or volunteers from using personal devices (e.g., smartphones, laptops) to access, process, transmit, or store any taxpayer information that is subject to restrictions on disclosure.</p><p>&nbsp;</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
